\f2\fs20 \cf0 This year's crop of nominees for Pittsburgh Technology Council's Tech 50 Awards will have a chance to show gala attendees not only who they are, but what they do.
\f3\fs24 \

\f2\fs20 Finalists will showcase their company's work and mission during the Tech 50 Showcase of Innovation, which will take place before the awards gala at the Wyndham Grand Pittsburgh Downtown on Nov. 1. The council will also recognize its 30-year anniversary with a review of what's happened in the region's tech sector over the course of three decades.
\f3\fs24 \

